Subject: [PATCH 2/6] Port drastic.sdl commits from 5ae9581e to a1c9aa6b

This includes 20 commits with the following features:
- Drastic-specific rendering optimizations
- Menu translation support
- Screen rotation support from layout.json
- Transparent bottom screen support
- Layout definitions for various resolutions
- Pixel filter toggle
- Theme switching support
- Alpha and position handling improvements
- D-pad input rotation based on screen rotation
- Settings menu (M key) for alpha/position/pixel/layout/theme
- And other drastic-specific enhancements
